                     <msItem xml:id="p1_i6">
                        <locus from="97va" to="105va" facs="0122"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3086RepCh366">Prayer to Our Lady Mary</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ኦመሠረት፡ አንቲ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ዓለም። ዘኮንኪ፡ ማኅደር፡ ለዓቢይ፡ ወልዑል፡ አምላክ፡ ወአጽልሊ፡ ላዕሌየ፡ ጽላሌ፡ ኣልባስኪ፨ 
                              <sic>ኣስመ፡</sic>
                            አምላክ፡ ጸልዪ፡ ላዕለ፡ እለ፡ 
                        
                              <sic>ይጸውዑ፡</sic>
                            ቅዱሰ፡ ስመኪ፨ ኦስብሕት፡ ወቡርክት፡ እምኵሎን፡ አንስት፡ እስእለኪ፡ ወ<supplied reason="omitted">ኣ</supplied>ስተበቍዓኪ፡ 
                        መሐርኒ፡ በሠናይ፡ ምግባርኪ፨
                     </incipit>
                        <note>The title is erased. The prayer terminates as in <ref type="item" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet17#ms_i2"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BAVet17#ms_i2</span></ref>.</note>
                        <colophon xml:lang="gez" xml:id="coloph1">
                           <locus target="#105vb" facs="0130"/>
                           ተፈጸመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ፻፹ወ፯ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ 
                              <sic>ወተፍጻሚታሂ፡</sic>
                            በወርሃ፡ 
                           
                              <sic>ጳጉሜ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>።</sic>
                            ወጸሓፊሓኒ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወል<supplied reason="omitted">ደ፡</supplied> 
                           ቀጦራሬ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ 
                              <sic>ለመድ<supplied reason="omitted">ኀ</supplied>ኒተ፡</sic>
                            ነፍሱ።
                           <note>The colophon states that the book was written in the year of mercy <date>187</date>, year of Luke, in the month of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ṗāgʷǝmen</foreign>, 
                            corresponding to the year <date>1536 AD</date>. The colophon also mentions the name of the scribe, 
                            <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10372Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs of Qaṭorāre</persName> (cp. <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/2FPWFRHU"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Fiaccadori1989Aethiopica"/><title level="a">Aethiopica minima</title><title level="j">Quaderni Utinensi</title><author><forename>Gianfranco</forename><surname>Fiaccadori</surname></author><date>1989</date><biblScope unit="volume">7 (13/14)</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">145-164</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Fiaccadori1989Aethiopica</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Fiaccadori1989Aethiopica</note><citedRange unit="item">160 n. 19</citedRange></bibl>).
                         </note>
                        </colophon>
                     </msItem>
                  
